++
++- **UUID generation**: Uses `github.com/google/uuid`
++- **HTTP handling**: Uses `github.com/gofiber/fiber/v2`
++- **DSL parsing**: Uses `github.com/antlr4-go/antlr/v4`
++- **MongoDB integration**: Uses `go.mongodb.org/mongo-driver/bson`
