++                  --status-code "ACTIVE"
++```
++
++Key fields:
++- `organization-id`: The parent organization's ID
++- `name`: Descriptive name for the ledger
++- `status-code`: Status of the ledger (usually "ACTIVE")
++
++Store the ledger ID:
++```bash
