+
+**Endpoint**: `PATCH /organizations/{organization_id}/ledgers/{ledger_id}/transactions/{transaction_id}`
+
+**Path Parameters**:
+- `organization_id` (string, required): Organization identifier
+- `ledger_id` (string, required): Ledger identifier
