+
+```bash
+git clone https://github.com/LerianStudio/midaz
+cd midaz
+```
+
+### 2. Set Up Environment Variables
+
+The Midaz system uses environment variables for configuration. Default environment files are provided as templates.
+
+```bash
+make set-env
